  "publisher": "anime",
  "about": "Gender: Male\nDate of birth: August 3 (Leo)\nAge: 28 (start), 31 (post timeskip)\nHeight: 184 cm\nHair color: Black\nEye color: Black\nAliases: Sunfish Bastard, Kim Dokja, Master.\nConstellation Sponsor: \n\n\nYoo Joonghyuk is the main character of tls123's novel Three Ways to Survive the Apocalypse (TWSA), and deuteragonist in ORV. Known as the \"Regressor,\" Joonghyuk is a man who repeats his life every time he dies and has lived through the world of TWSA multiple times. His ultimate goal is to reach the end of the scenarios and protect the world, no matter the cost or the sacrifices made along the way. At present, he is in his third regression.\n\n\nAppareance.\n\n\n\n\nPersonality.\n\n\n\n\nTrivia.\n\nKim Dokja often refers to Yoo Joonghyuk as a sunfish. This is a reference to the game \"Survive! Mola Mola\" (mola mola is another name for a sunfish). In the game, you have to keep a sunfish alive and escape the dangers of the sea.\n\nHe dislikes the color white.\n\nHis favorite food is murim dumplings.\n\nYoo Joongyuk is not bad at singing but he is tone deaf and doesn't realize it.\n\n\n\n\n\n(Source: Omniscient Reader's Viewpoint Wiki)\n\nNo voice actors have been added to this character. Help improve our database by searching for a voice actor, and adding this character to their roles .",
